<span id="freeTextContainer14839840652414646486">This is one of my favorite books. The daughter of Clifton Fadiman can write! These are wonderful essays about life, family, and most importantly, about books &amp; reading. All are interesting &amp; written beautifully, and they also have a lot of warmth &amp; humor. This is a book worth owning to be able to reread certain essays every once in a while.<br/><br/>This book is a perfect gift for anyone who enjoys reading, books, and language.</span>

